flowchart TD
    FeasibleList[Feasible Nodes List] --> LoopNodes[Iterate over Feasible Nodes]
    
    subgraph Scoring Plugins
        direction LR
        ImageLocality[ImageLocalityPlugin<br/>Weight: 1]
        BalancedAllocation[NodeResourcesBalancedAllocation<br/>Weight: 1]
        NodeAffinity[NodeAffinityPriorityPlugin<br/>Weight: 2]
        TSpread[PodTopologySpreadPriorityPlugin<br/>Weight: 2]
    end

    LoopNodes --> ImageLocality
    LoopNodes --> BalancedAllocation
    LoopNodes --> NodeAffinity
    LoopNodes --> TSpread

    ImageLocality -->|Score: 0-100| Combine
    BalancedAllocation -->|Score: 0-100| Combine
    NodeAffinity -->|Score: 0-100| Combine
    TSpread -->|Score: 0-100| Combine

    subgraph Score Accumulator
        Combine[Score * Weight sum per Node] --> Normalize[Normalize scores 0 to 100]
    end

    Normalize --> SelectMax[Select Node with Highest Score]
    SelectMax --> TieBreaker{Tie breaker needed?}
    TieBreaker -->|Yes| RoundRobin[Deterministic Round-Robin Selection]
    TieBreaker -->|No| Bind[Assign Pod to Selected Node]
    RoundRobin --> Bind
